title: FILA - Men's Short Sleeve Tennis Performance Polo Shirt
descriptionHtml:
Unleash your style with the Tennis Performance polo shirt, the perfect combination of personality and dynamic sports style. Designed with a classic fit and FILA logo printed on the left chest, you can comfortably transform your daily style, whether at the practice court or during casual outings with friends.
 
Brand: Fila
Origin: South Korea
Gender: Men
Style: Polo shirt
Color: Ink Navy, White
Material: TBD
Classic fit, short sleeves
Pattern: Solid color
Design:
  • Shoulders and sleeve cuffs designed with contrasting tone colors
  • Simple round buttons
  • Refined stitching
  • Soft, flexible material suitable for all circumstances
  • Modern, youthful colors that easily match with many other outfits
Logo: Printed on the left chest
Shirt fit: Loose and comfortable
Suitable for occasions: Casual outings, work...
Seasonal trend: Can be used well in all seasons of the year
